info:
Graphic Artist who is currently studying Sound Engineering and has taken as a hobby to remix tracks relevant to the Demoscene due to personal interest.
HaasiD was influenced by the scene since very young, as such, she has an unexplained fetish for the Commodore 64 and even suggested to put an altar up to the ones she has in her home.
Here is her graphic art site: [url]http://haashiaos.deviantart.com[/url]
